channel.title: Need help with changing home
channel.description: I'm using the PKPlanet source, and I'm trying to find out how to make the home teleport send you somewhere else instead of edgeville, and I want to make it so that new players are also in the new home location upon account creation. When i teleport to home i get "50235" and i think that might lead somewhere. If anyone knows how to change the teleport coordinates and the coordinates for when new players log in, please let me know
